---

### 🔍 What We Do

**AI-Augmented Pentesting**
Leverage LLM-driven reconnaissance, intelligent fuzzing, and exploit reasoning to uncover vulnerabilities at scale.
From static code analysis to dynamic application testing, our AI agents continuously learn from real-world vulnerabilities and adapt to new targets.

**Automated Bug Bounty Intelligence**
Aggregate, prioritize, and analyze disclosed CVEs, bug bounty reports, and exploit PoCs.
Our models extract attack patterns, build knowledge graphs of vulnerabilities, and predict exploitable components before attackers do.

**Security Copilot for Researchers**
An interactive LLM-based assistant trained on thousands of public pentests, exploit databases, and source code repositories — built to accelerate your research workflow, code auditing, and payload development.

**Adversarial AI Research**
We explore how AI models themselves can become targets — analyzing prompt injection, model inversion, and data poisoning attacks — ensuring both offensive and defensive resilience.

